# AI Resume Screening System

> An AI-powered Applicant Tracking System (ATS) that analyzes, ranks, and compares candidate resumes against a job description using semantic similarity, skill matching, and resume analysis.

![Python](https://img.shields.io/badge/Python-3.12-blue)
![Streamlit](https://img.shields.io/badge/Streamlit-1.59-red)
![Sentence Transformers](https://img.shields.io/badge/Sentence--Transformers-NLP-green)
![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-success)

---

## Overview

Recruiters often spend significant time manually reviewing resumes to identify suitable candidates. This project automates that process by leveraging Natural Language Processing (NLP) and semantic embeddings to compare resumes with a job description.

The system extracts candidate information, evaluates resume relevance using semantic similarity, calculates an ATS score, identifies skill gaps, ranks candidates, and generates professional PDF reports.

The application is built with a modular architecture using Python and Streamlit, making it easy to maintain and extend.

---

## Features

### Resume Processing

- Upload multiple resumes (PDF)
- Upload Job Description (PDF)
- Automatic text extraction
- Candidate information extraction
- Education parsing
- Experience extraction
- Skill extraction

---

### AI Resume Analysis

- Semantic similarity matching using Sentence Transformers
- ATS score calculation
- Skill match percentage
- Missing skills identification
- Candidate ranking
- AI-generated candidate summary
- Hiring recommendation

---

### Interactive Dashboard

- Candidate ranking table
- Search candidates
- Filter by degree
- Filter by experience
- Filter by ATS score
- Interactive charts
- CSV export

---

### Candidate Details

- Personal information
- Education details
- Performance metrics
- Skills analysis
- AI-generated summary
- Resume feedback

---

### Candidate Comparison

- Compare any two candidates
- ATS score comparison
- Experience comparison
- Skill match comparison
- Side-by-side analysis

---

### Professional PDF Reports

Generate recruiter-ready reports containing:

- Candidate Information
- Education
- Performance Scores
- Skills Analysis
- AI Candidate Summary
- Hiring Recommendation
- Page numbering
- Professional formatting

